In this task, I created a one-page infographic to explain the concept of digital literacy and its importance for students. I used Canva to design a visually appealing layout that included key topics such as safe internet practices, digital tools for learning, and maintaining a professional online presence. The goal was to make the information simple, engaging, and easy to understand for my peers. While designing, I learned how to present complex ideas in a visual format. This task improved my creativity and helped me understand how digital awareness can be effectively communicated through design.
